577
00:51:13,760 --> 00:51:19,280
[SPEAKER_01] Čovječe, kaže: tek sad postajem pravi sljedbenik isca Krista.

578
00:51:19,440 --> 00:51:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] tek sad postajem njegov učenik.

579
00:51:21,360 --> 00:51:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] U zatvoru kad sprema se da ga upiju.

580
00:51:26,719 --> 00:51:27,199
