1441
01:59:31,840 --> 01:59:33,359
[SPEAKER_02] Da će biti dobro.

1442
01:59:34,640 --> 01:59:35,039
[SPEAKER_02] Bit će dobro.

1443
01:59:35,439 --> 01:59:35,840
[SPEAKER_02] Bit će dobro.

1444
01:59:36,079 --> 01:59:39,760
[SPEAKER_02] Poruka za kraj svetog Filipa Nerija: budite dobri.

1445
01:59:40,319 --> 01:59:41,279
