1452
01:59:51,840 --> 01:59:54,640
[SPEAKER_01] Mislio sam da ću kratko, ali očito to u meni ne može.

1453
01:59:56,319 --> 01:59:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ostala je navika, zbriga, možda.

1454
01:59:58,720 --> 01:59:59,920
